==German==

===Etymology===
From {{inh|de|gmh|sameztac|sameztac, samztac}}, from {{inh|de|goh|sambaztag||Sabbath day}}, from {{der|de|got|*𐍃𐌰𐌼𐌱𐌰𐍄𐍉}}, an alteration (possibly dialectal) of earlier, Biblical {{m|got|𐍃𐌰𐌱𐌱𐌰𐍄𐍉}}, from {{der|de|gkm|σάμβατον||Sabbath}} (compare {{cog|fr|samedi}}, {{cog|fro|sambedi}}, {{cog|rm|somda}}, {{cog|ro|sâmbătă}}, {{cog|hu|szombat}}).

